A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
The NAG conducts rapid, secure, and independent assessments of critical and unique technologies to support the Military Services, other government agencies, and
DTRA. This rapid assessment group provides independent assessments of critical and unique technologies and capabilities for customers in the areas of counter WMD
and emerging threats. The NAG provides an independent review/analysis and reporting of operational assessments, capability demonstrations, and test events.

