The FNC Program favors a high level of collaboration. PE R-2 activities are mostly organized by the Office of
Naval Research (ONR) Departments, which are tasked to collaborate with the acquisition stakeholders and their
resource sponsors.

A complete accounting of the technology candidates being developed and a full disposition of each technology
development effort funded in this PE is provided annually to the Congressional oversight committees.

FY 2025 Plans:
- Complete focused research in the area of Signature Management.
- Complete research effort to support multi-domain sensing of the electronic spectrum.
- Complete applied research in the area of integration and automated collaboration as a function of command
