- Air vehicle flying qualities and control.
- High lift aerodynamics and control.
- Vertical/Short Take-off and Landing (V/STOL) science & technology.
- Automated launch and recovery technology.
- Mechanical/environmental failure prediction research.
- Advanced dynamics and topology of coupled human/machine systems.
- Precise relative navigation science & technology.
