The funding applies to the design, systems engineering, prototyping, and vendor qualification activities needed to execute the schedule for Common Missile
Compartment (CMC) design, whole ship design, and component technologies development for the next generation U.S. ballistic missile submarine (SSBN), the
COLUMBIA Class.

