       Change Summary Explanation
       The FY 2026 request was reduced by $0.118 million for Advisory and Assistance Services to promote efficiencies and advance the policies of the Administration
       in alignment with Executive Order 14222, "Implementing the President's Department of Government Efficiency Cost Efficiency Initiative."

       FY 2026 programmatic increases for Project 3018 and Project 3155: Project 3018 enhanced Defense Cyber Operational capabilities at critical sites and the
       development of More Situational Awareness (MOSAICS). Project 3155 increase is to support the continuation, integration, and successful completion of C-
       UxS and Blue Robotic and Autonomous Systems (RAS). These efforts utilized agile management methods for Force Protection, covering labor, software, and
       hardware costs while increasing the likelihood of successful transition.




